resource.name: ricentities
resource.title: RICentites
resource.description: RICentites are the unified nomencalture of trade reporting and partner names.

fields.name: RICname
fields.description: name of the RICentities (unique identifier)

fields.name: type
fields.description: RICentity type: city/part_of, colonial_area, country, geographical_area, group

fields.name: continent
fields.description: continent the RICentity belongs to (Ocean are considered as continents).

fields.name: GPH_code
fields.description: GeoPolHist dataset identifier mostly compatible with Correlates Of War (COW) identifiers.

fields.name: slug
fields.description: slug

fields.name: part_of_GPH_entity

resource.name: flows

sources.title: Trade statistics from various countries archives and research papers, see data/sources.csv for details

resource.title: Trade flows transcribed from various international trade statistics volumes

fields.name: source
fields.description: The source document this trade flow was extracted from

fields.name: flow
fields.description: value of the trade flow

fields.name: unit
fields.description: The unit the trade flow value is expressed in

fields.name: currency
fields.description: The currency the trade flow value is expressed in

fields.name: year
fields.description: The year of the trade flow

fields.name: reporting
fields.description: Name of the country reporting the trade flow

fields.name: partner
fields.description: Name of the trade partner of the trade flow

fields.name: export_import
fields.description: Precise wether this trade flow is an importation or exportation.

fields.name: special_general
fields.description: Precise wether this trade flow is of type special or general.

fields.name: species_bullions
fields.description: Precise wether this trade flow is a monatory flow.

fields.name: transport_type
fields.description: For some flows, the transport type is precised : by land or by see for instance.

fields.name: statistical_period
fields.description: Some statistics are not reported by civil years. This field indicates those precising the statistical period (not normalized).

fields.name: partner_sum
fields.description: When '1', indicates trade flows which are subtotals calculated in the source (this field should be a boolean...).

fields.name: world_trade_type
fields.description: Categorize the different types of Total trade calculations: total_estimated (recent estimations), total_reporting1 (total reported by the soruce), total_reporting2 (subtotals reported by the source)

fields.name: notes
fields.description: Free text notes left by the research team
